something. But I'll call on you to introduce yourself and add some context. And then third,

00:02:38.320 --> 00:02:43.440
we have a Slido link where you can ask questions anonymously. And I see Curtis was right on top of

00:02:43.440 --> 00:02:51.279
it and shared it there in the chat. I guess one more note to share, we do have a LinkedIn group.

